Day 5: Compliance and Auditing
Overview
This section will focus on the importance of compliance with various standards and how to audit your application security effectively.
Objectives
‚Ä¢	Understand the significance and requirements of PCI DSS and ISO standards in application security.
‚Ä¢	Apply auditing techniques to evaluate the security posture of applications.
‚Ä¢	Analyze reports to make informed decisions for enhancing application security.
Detailed Topics and Activities
1. PCI DSS Compliance
‚Ä¢	Understanding: Lecture on what PCI DSS is and why it's crucial for application security.
‚Ä¢	Application: Hands-on lab to implement PCI DSS compliant features in a sample application.
‚Ä¢	Auditor's Method: Checklist of PCI DSS requirements and how to audit them.
‚Ä¢	Developer's Strategy: Implementing encryption, secure authentication, and regular security assessments.
‚Ä¢	Code Snippet for PCI DSS Compliance in Java:
javaCopy code
if (cardData.isEncrypted() && user.isPCICompliant()) { // Proceed with the transaction } 
2. ISO Standards in Application Security
‚Ä¢	Understanding: Introduction to ISO standards like ISO/IEC 27001 and their importance in application security.
‚Ä¢	Application: Hands-on lab to implement ISO-compliant security features.
‚Ä¢	Auditor's Method: Using ISO frameworks for security audits.
‚Ä¢	Developer's Strategy: Implementing secure coding practices as per ISO standards.
‚Ä¢	Guide for ISO Compliance: ISO/IEC 27001 Compliance Guide
3. Security Auditing and Reporting
‚Ä¢	Understanding: Lecture on the significance of regular security audits and effective reporting.
‚Ä¢	Application: Hands-on lab on conducting a security audit and generating reports.
‚Ä¢	Auditor's Method: Using automated tools and manual checks for a comprehensive audit.
‚Ä¢	Developer's Strategy: Regularly reviewing audit reports and updating security measures.
‚Ä¢	Real-World Example: Case study on how a major financial institution improved its security posture through rigorous auditing.
Real-World Examples and Case Studies
‚Ä¢	Case Study on PCI DSS Compliance: How a major e-commerce platform achieved compliance.
